NAME

    Keyword::Simple - define new keywords in pure Perl

INSTALLATION

    To download and install this module, use your favorite CPAN client, e.g.
    "cpan":

        cpan Keyword::Simple

    Or "cpanm":

        cpanm Keyword::Simple

    To do it manually, run the following commands (after downloading and
    unpacking the tarball):

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

    After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
    "perldoc" command.

        perldoc Keyword::Simple

    You can also look for information at
    <https://metacpan.org/pod/Keyword::Simple>.

    To see a list of open bugs, visit
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Keyword-Simple>.

    To report a new bug, send an email to "bug-Keyword-Simple [at]
    rt.cpan.org".

